18:36.524 --> 18:39.787
It's why my people wandered
the desert for 40 years.

18:39.789 --> 18:42.523
Took that long to walk it off.

18:44.124 --> 18:46.256
You see, Penny, the Israelites
were in the desert...

18:46.258 --> 18:48.663
Shut up!

18:48.665 --> 18:51.696
So glad you two
are done fighting.

18:51.698 --> 18:56.303
Right now, I'm just trying
to burp without throwing up.

18:56.305 --> 18:57.367
SHELDON:
Hang on.

18:57.369 --> 19:00.341
<i>Physics Today</i>
mentioned the paper.

19:00.343 --> 19:01.436
What'd they say?

19:01.438 --> 19:03.835
Who cares?
Did they mention Leonard?

19:03.837 --> 19:04.938
They did.

